data.description: This is the home you'e been waiting for in Jacksonville. This spacious home has recently been updated with fresh interior paint and all new windows. The pool is approximately 2 years old and is located in a lovely level, fenced yard. Inside this home has a great floor plan, with a study on the main level, 4 bedrooms (master on main level) and a little nook upstairs. You'll love the dining room with a coffered ceiling. Make your appointment today! Check out the "VIRTUAL TOUR" 360 tour link on this listing.
